## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **Rebyota 2022-11 + Vowst 2023-04** = first FDA microbiome therapeutics. 둘 다 rCDI 한정 적응증. 1990년대부터 compassionate FMT 가 있었지만 정식 FDA approval 까지 30년. quantum-VQE 의 직접 fit 한정 (community-level modality 가 small-molecule binding 과 다른 paradigm).
2. **SYNB1618/1934 PKU FAILED Phase 3 2023** (Synlogic) = first engineered LBP for monogenic disease 시도 → 실패. mfg + dose-response + colonization-persistence 가 limiting factor. quantum-VQE scope 외부.
3. **Pfizer ClostriDose C. diff vaccine FAILED 2022** = vaccine 기반 1차예방 실패. microbiome restoration 이 더 compelling path. cross-vacc.
4. **fidaxomicin (Dificid) 2011 + bezlotoxumab (Zinplava) 2016** = microbiome-preserving path: narrow-spectrum + toxin-targeted. quantum-VQE 의 RNA polymerase + TcdB Fab 표적 fit.
5. **Akkermansia muciniphila + cancer immunotherapy responder** = Routy 2018 / Gopalakrishnan 2018. consortium 기반 IO augmentation 임상 trial 진행 중. cross-cancer.
6. **MTT autism trial (Kang 2017 → 2019 Sloan-Kettering controversial)** = autism MGB axis 임상 효과 mixed. small-N + open-label heterogeneity. ethical scope (vulnerable population).
7. **bacteriophage therapy = pre-antibiotic era → MDR-AMR era 부활** = Soviet legacy + 2010s+ Western IND 부활 (compassionate). quantum-VQE 의 phage RBP + 박테리아 surface 가 hxq-mb-phage-001 candidate motivation.
8. **vonoprazan Voquezna 2022 PCAB** = H. pylori 신규 PCAB class FDA. cross-GI. PPI 보다 better-acid-control + microbiome 영향 비슷 (open).
9. **H. pylori triple/quadruple therapy classical** = clarithromycin resistance 증가 + microbiome wreckage. 신규 microbiome-sparing 항-H. pylori 가 hxq-mb-hp-001 candidate motivation.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, microbiome 임상 의미 한정 (community-level modality 가 fundamentally wet).

